    "Description": "This check validates the health and concurrency stability of indexes used in In-Memory OLTP (XTP) tables. High values for `page_update_retry_count` indicate frequent internal conflicts or resource contention during Data Manipulation Language (DML) operations, which severely degrades performance and scalability. Monitoring these statistics is crucial for maintaining high throughput in memory-optimized environments.",
